Tac instructions:

- Title screen: type the number correspondent of the map on the menu

- Game screen: 
  - Left click on a player unit to select it
  - Right click on a computer unit to attack it
  - With an unit selected, left click in a passable square to move the unit to that square
  - Use the mouse scroll to zoom in or zoom out
  - Use the keyboard arrows to move the map
  - Escape goes back to the title screen
